"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2806
#, no-c-format
msgid "&pdflatex;"
msgstr "&pdflatex;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2808
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There is also another way to compile your document, if you want a PDF: "
#| "you can run &pdflatex;, that will compile the source directly into a PDF "
#| "file, with <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>6</keycap></keycombo>: you can then "
#| "view the compiled file pressing <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>7</keycap></"
#| "keycombo>."
msgid ""
"There is also another way to compile your document, if you want a PDF: you "
"can run &pdflatex;, that will compile the source directly into a PDF file, "
"with <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>6</keycap></keycombo>: you can then view the "
"compiled file by pressing <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>7</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Dokumenti saab veel ühel moel kompileerida, kui  soovid saada PDF-faili: "
"käivita &pdflatex;, mis kompileerib lähteteksti otse PDF-failiks, "
"kiirklahviga <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>6</keycap></keycombo>. Seejärel võib "
"kompileeritud faili vaadata kiirklahviga <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>7</keycap></"
"keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2813
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Alternatively, you can convert a PS into a PDF with <keycombo>&Alt;"
#| "<keycap>8</keycap></keycombo>, or directly a &DVI; into a PDF with "
#| "<keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>9</keycap></keycombo>."
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can convert a PS into a PDF with <keycombo>&Alt;"
"<keycap>8</keycap></keycombo>, or a &DVI; directly into a PDF with "
"<keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>9</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Teine võimalus on teisendada PS-fail PDF-failiks kiirklahviga <keycombo>&Alt;"
"<keycap>8</keycap></keycombo> või &DVI;-fail otse PDF-failiks kiirklahviga "
"<keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>9</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2817
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Using &pdflatex; instead of &latex; may be just a matter of simplicity or "
#| "habit, but sometimes the behavior of the two program can differ."
msgid ""
"Using &pdflatex; instead of &latex; may be just a matter of simplicity or "
"habit, but sometimes the behavior of the two programs can differ."
msgstr ""
"&pdflatex;i eelistamine &latex;ile võib olla lihtsuse või harjumuse küsimus, "
"kuid kohati on kahe programmi käitumine üpris erinev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2824
#, no-c-format
msgid "&latex; to Web"
msgstr "&latex; veebis"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2826
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, you may want to publish your work on the web and not just on paper. "
"You may then use the <application>latex2html</application> program, that can "
"be called from &kile;'s menu <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Convert</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>LaTeX to Web</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. The result will be placed in a subfolder of the "
"work folder, and you will be able to see the result of the conversion "
"choosing the menu item <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>View</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>View &HTML;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Sul võib olla ka soov avaldada oma töö veebis, mitte aga paberil. Selleks "
"saab kasutada programmi <application>latex2html</application>, mille saab "
"käivitada &kile; menüükäsuga <menuchoice><guimenu>Ehitamine</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Teisendamine</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>LaTeX -> HTML</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Tulemus asetatakse sinu töökataloogi "
"alamkataloogi, teisenduse saadust võid näha menüükäsuga "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Ehitamine</guimenu><guisubmenu>Vaatamine</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Vaata &HTML;-i</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2838
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Passing Command-Line Parameters"
msgid "Passing Command Line Parameters"
msgstr "Käsurea parameetrid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2840
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you want to pass some specific command-line parameters to the compile, "
#| "convert or view tools, you can configure their call in "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</"
#| "guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Tools</guisubmenu><guilabel>Build</guilabel></"
#| "menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"If you want to pass some specific command line parameters to the compile, "
"convert or view tools, you can configure their call in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Tools</guisubmenu><guilabel>Build</guilabel></"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Võib juhtuda, et soovid anda töövahenditele oma failide kompileerimiseks, "
"teisendamiseks või vaatamiseks mõningaid spetsiaalseid käsureaparameetreid. "
"Standardseid tööriistu saab seadistada menüükäsuga "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Kile seadistamine...</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Tööriistad</guisubmenu><guilabel>Ehitamine</"
"guilabel></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2849
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Quick Preview</title>"
msgstr "<title>Kiire eelvaatlus</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will always need some time to view the result, when working with "
"&latex;. &latex; has to compile the source and the viewer has to be called. "
"This can be annoying if you only changed some letters in an equation "
"difficult to typeset. &kile; offers a <emphasis>Quick Preview</emphasis> "
"mode, where you can compile only a part of a document and save a lot of "
"time. It supports four different modes, which can be combined with seven "
"configurations."
msgstr ""
"&latex;iga töötades tuleb alati leida aega oma töö tulemuse uurimiseks. "
"&latex; peab kompileerima lähteteksti ning välja kutsuma dokumendi näitaja. "
"See võib olla tülikas, kui oled muutnud näiteks ainult mõnda tähte "
"võrrandis. &kile; pakub selleks välja <emphasis>kiire eelvaatluse</emphasis> "
"režiimi, kus kompileeritakse ainult osa dokumendist, mis säästab tublisti "
"aega. Toetatud on neli erinevat režiimi, mida saab omavahel kombineerida "
"seitsme seadistusega."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2859
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Quick Preview</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Kiire eelvaatlus</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2865
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Quick Preview</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kiire eelvaatlus</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All settings must be done in <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Tools</"
"guimenuitem><guilabel>Preview</guilabel></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Kõiki seadistusi saab määrata ja muuta, kui valida "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kile seadistamine...</"
"guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Tööriistad</guimenuitem><guilabel>Eelvaatlus</"
"guilabel></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2875
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Quick Preview Configuration</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Kiire eelvaatluse seadistamine</screeninfo>"

